ide.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERetireGuide%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20consumers%20should%20evaluate%20their%20risk%20tolerance%20before%20making%20any%20changes%20to%20where%20and%20how%20they%20save%20and%20invest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20could%20make%20sense%20to%20consider%20different%20savings%20products%20than%20you're%20using%20now%2C%20either%20before%20or%20after%20rates%20drop.%20For%20example%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fbest-5-year-cd-rates%5C%22%3E5-year%20certificates%20of%20deposit%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20pay%20less%20than%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fbest-1-year-cd-rates%5C%22%3E1-year%20CD%3C%2Fa%3E%20right%20now%2C%20but%20that%20may%20not%20be%20true%20in%20the%20future%20if%20the%20Fed%20cuts%20interest%20rates%20several%20times%20over%20the%20coming%20months%20and%20years.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fcd-ladder%5C%22%3ELaddering%20CDs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20bonds%2C%20or%20fixed%20annuities%20can%20also%20act%20as%20a%20middle%20ground%20for%20those%20who%20need%20to%20balance%20liquidity%20with%20returns%2C%20said%20Kates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20advisor%20also%20says%20investors%20with%20a%20higher%20risk%20tolerance%20and%20long-term%20investment%20horizon%20can%20consider%20allocating%20more%20funds%20toward%20stocks%20and%20other%20equities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCertain%20sectors%20such%20as%20utilities%2C%20real%20estate%2C%20and%20consumer%20discretionary%20tend%20to%20perform%20especially%20well%20during%20rate-cutting%20cycles%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E3.%20Reconsider%20large%2C%20financed%20purchases%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFinancial%20advisor%20Cliff%20Ambrose%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapex-wealth.net%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApex%20Wealth%3C%2Fa%3E%2