ork-young-pros-cons-not-worth-it-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebased%20in%20New%20York%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20had%20an%20outfit%20planned%20for%20the%2030th%20anniversary%20of%20The%20Little%20Mermaid%2C%20and%20I%20learned%20that%20Leo%20had%20a%20shtick%20of%20dressing%20up%20as%20Prince%20Eric%2C%20and%20we%20did%20a%20photo%20shoot%20together%20on%20the%20cruise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20hitting%20it%20off%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20stay%20in%20contact%20as%20friends.%20Facetimes%20and%20consistent%20communication%20allowed%20us%20to%20really%20get%20to%20know%20each%20other%2C%20and%20I%20started%20feeling%20sparks.%20About%20a%20month%20after%20we%20first%20met%2C%20I%20was%20in%20LA%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoachella-midlife-crisis-at-55-essay-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECoachella%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I%20decided%20to%20stay%20a%20few%20extra%20days%20to%20see%20Leo.%20Our%20first%20date%20was%20at%20a%20Mexican%20barcade%20in%20LA%2C%20where%20we%20really%20got%20to%20dig%20deep%2C%20and%20I%20just%20felt%20such%20a%20connection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20year%2C%20we%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20travel%20back%20and%20forth%20to%20see%20each%20other.%20While%20the%20first%20year%20of%20our%20relationship%20may%20have%20been%20non-traditional%2C%20we%20really%20had%20to%20jump%20in%20because%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-only-been-long-distance-relationships-whole-life-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elong-distance%20relationships%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20visiting%20your%20partner%20means%20essentially%20living%20with%20them%20while%20you're%20there.%20When%20the%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20being%20in%20New%20York%20was%20a%20particularly%20scary%20experience%2C%20and%20I%20told%20Leo%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20love%20to%20come%20and%20stay%20with%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20to%20which%20he%20agreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeo%20and%20I%20met%20later%20in%20life%2C%