%3EMullinix%20noted%20that%20some%20employers%20are%20shifting%20to%20contract%20and%20freelance%20work%20to%20avoid%20taking%20on%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20full-time%20worker%20who%20would%20get%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20overall%20unemployment%20rate%20remains%20low%2C%20and%20there%20are%20still%20areas%20where%20employers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-growing-jobs-desperate-to-hire-salaries-openings-demand-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecan't%20find%20the%20talent%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20need.%20Plus%2C%20parts%20of%20the%20economy%20could%20further%20heat%20up%2C%20particularly%20after%20the%20Federal%20Reserve's%20decision%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-cuts-interest-rates-how-much-september-fomc-powell-inflation-2024-9%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAn%2520interest%252Drate%2520cut%2520has%2Ccut%2520rates%2520since%2520March%25202020.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecut%20interest%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20four%20years%20following%20an%20effort%20to%20stamp%20out%20high%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2230333d15-efdd-4b41-b857-76b63a4ce4ad%5C%22%3EStartups%20could%20give%20a%20boost%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAtli%20Thorkelsson%2C%20who%20helps%20startups%20recruit%20at%20the%20venture%20capital%20firm%20Redpoint%20Ventures%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20he%20expects%20startup%20hiring%20will%20prove%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20active%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20second%20half%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20hearing%20a%20lot%20from%20recruiting%20firms%20that%20they're%20super%20busy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20seeing%20an%20uptick%20in%20search%20requests%20coming%20from%20our%20founders%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThorkelsson%20said%20hiring%20at%20startups%20began%20to%20pick%20up%20last%20September%20and%20that%20for%20many%20small%20companies%2C%20growth%20was%20cautious%20but%20notable%20in%20terms%20of%20demand%20for%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20in%20other%20corners%20of%20the%20economy%2C%20employers'%20wariness%20is%20winning%20out%20%E2%80%94%20for%20now.%20That's%20causing%20some%20to%20list%20fewer%20job%20openings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompanies%20are%20being%20more%20cautious%2C%26quot%3B%20Mullinix%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20challenge%20is%20that%20with%20fewer%20openings%2C%20the%20number%20of%20applicants%20per%20role%20can%20stack%20up%2C%20he%20said.%20That%20can%20make%20it%20harder%20for%20job%20seekers%2C%20of%20course%2C%20and%20for%20recruiters%20who%20have%20to%20sift%20through%20a%20pile%20of%20applications.%20Big%20companies%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20tend%20to%20use%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresume-too-long-how-to-fix-it-job-search-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoftware%20to%20sort%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20high%20number%20of%20applicants%20can%20lead%20to%20some%20tough%20decisions%2C%20Mullinix%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecruiters%20are%20%26quot%3Bscreening%20a%20little%20bit%20harder%20so%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20go%20through%201%2C000%20applications%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BRealistically%2C%20they%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20do%20that%20in%20a%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20though%20the%20unemployment%20rate%20is%20low%2C%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20only%20those%20without%20work%20are%20thumbing%20through%20job%20listings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20the%20people%20that%20are%20currently%20in%20jobs%20are%20not%20happy%20with%20the%20jobs%20that%20they%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20Mullinix%20said.%20He%20said%20inflation%20has%20left%20some%20workers%20upset%20that%20their%20wages%20haven't%20always%20kept%20up%20with%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20as%20people%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-stay-workplace-productivity-points-to-economic-growth-jobs-loyalty2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estaying%20in%20jobs%20longer%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20only%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20ago%20during%20the%20so-called%20Great%20Resignation%2C%20some%20of%20them%20are%20getting%20antsy%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20is%20you%20have%20job%20seekers%20that%20are%20both%20employed%20and%20then%20unemployed%2C%20searching%20at%20the%20same%20time%20in%20a%20market%20where%20the%20supply%20is%20down%20and%20the%20demand%20is%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Mullinix%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20especially%20true%20with%20high-paying%20jobs%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f812511c-fa76-4ed2-80b7-42a1c32bd13a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20shotgun%20it%2C%20but%20don't%20hold%20back%20too%20much%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMullinix%20said%20it's%20possible%20to%20both%20apply%20to%20too%20many%20jobs%20%E2%80%94%20and%20not%20enough.%20He%20said%20the%20bulk%20approach%20of%20going%20for%20every%20job%20where%20applying%20is%20a%20single%20click%20often%20isn't%20as%20effective%20because%20so%20many%20people%20end%20up%20vying%20for%20the%20same%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20he%20said%2C%20it's%20wise%20to%20be%20more%20deliberate%20and%20choose%20the%20ones%20you%20might%20be%20best%20qualified%20for.%20Also%2C%20do%20the%20tedious%20work%20of%20filling%20out%20applications%20that%20aren't%20one%20click%2C%20Mullinix%20said.%20That%20often%20means%20wading%20through%20clunky%20software%20interfaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20same%20process%20everybody%20else%20has%20to%20go%20through%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20going%20to%20cut%20out%20some%20candidates%20right%20there%2C%20and%20that's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20less%20competitive%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20just%20because%20the%20job%20title%20in%20a%20posting%20might%20be%20different%20from%20one%20you've%20had%20before%2C%20it's%20often%20still%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20apply%20if%20you%20have%20the%20right%20skills%20and%20qualifications%2C%20Mullinix%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompanies%20name%20things%20100%20different%20ways%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMullinix%20said%20that%20given%20how%20unpleasant%20the%20search%20process%20can%20be%2C%20it's%20understandable%20that%20job%20seekers%20would%20gravitate%20toward%20the%20easiest%20method%20for%20applying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnline%20job%20seeking%20is%20just%20not%20the%20most%20fun%20activity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20it%20tends%20to%20rank%20poorly%20in%20surveys.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20pretty%20much%20next%20to%20being%20divorced%20on%20a%20scale%20of%20enjoyability.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhiring-picks-up-in-fall-low-openings-hurting-job-seekers-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727001782000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bcba9db4912df3ae1b8721%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhiring-picks-up-in-fall-low-openings-hurting-job-seekers-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20low%20unemployment%2C%20job%20openings%20in%20the%20US%20are%20at%20their%20lowest%20since%20early%202021.%20That%20could%20make%20fall%20hiring%20less%20robust%20than%20in%20previous%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tparadis%40businessinsider.com%20(Tim%20Paradis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhiring-picks-up-in-fall-low-openings-hurting-job-seekers-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20likely%20to%20clock%207%25%20growth%20in%20FY25%20despite%20headwinds%3A%20Deloitte%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727001575000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-12%2F17%2Fthumb%2Ffeature