n%20of%20the%20world%20would%20look%20like%2C%20we%20had%20no%20idea%20just%20how%20majestic%20and%20other-worldly%20it%20would%20be.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20started%20our%20journey%20with%20two%20overnights%20before%20getting%20on%20the%20ship%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223904%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22View%20of%20Longyearbyen%2C%20the%20northernmost%20town%20on%20the%20planet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e9805ecfb7f307e5723599%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222928%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20and%20her%20sister%20spent%20a%20night%20in%20Longyearbyen%2C%20the%20northernmost%20town%20with%20a%20population%20larger%20than%201%2C000%2C%20before%20embarking%20on%20their%20cruise.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Gail%20Abrams%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20first%20flew%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foslo-could-become-top-destination-after-unconventional-ad-goes-viral-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOslo%2C%20Norway%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20an%20overnight%20and%20then%20took%20a%20charter%20flight%20to%20Longyearbyen%2C%20the%20northernmost%20town%20in%20the%20world%2C%20for%20another%20overnight%20and%20land%20tour%20before%20boarding%20our%20ship.%20When%20we%20finally%20arrived%20in%20our%20stateroom%2C%20we%20were%20exhausted%20from%20almost%20three%20full%20days%20of%20travel%2C%20and%20our%20beds%20looked%20tempting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEvery%20day%20was%20an%20adventure%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223744%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Sylvia%20Earle%20ship%20in%20the%20water%20against%20a%20mountain%20with%20snow%20on%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e97b9ed17aa3c7b2b342e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222808%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20and%20her%20sister%20stayed%20on%20a%20ship%20named%20after%20renowned%20marine%20biologist%20and%20oceanographer%20Sylvia%20Earle.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Gail%20Abrams%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20we%20were%20immediately%20summoned%20to%20an%20orientation%20by%20the%20ship's%20Expedition%20Team%2C%20where%20we%20learned%20that%20one%20of%20the%20most%20thrilling%20aspects%20of%20these%20trips%20is%20that%20you%20never%20know%20exactly%20what%20each%20day%20will%20hold%2C%20but%20it's%20always%20guaranteed%20to%20be%20an%20adventure.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20afternoon%20before%20dinner%2C%20passengers%20and%20the%20expedition%20team%20gathered%20in%20the%20Lecture%20Lounge%20to%20review%20the%20next%20day's%20itinerary%2C%20knowing%20that%20things%20may%20change%20according%20to%20weather%20and%20wildlife%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EExpert%20guides%20took%20us%20exploring%20on%20Zodiacs%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Iceberg%20in%20water%20on%20a%20sunny%20day%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e97bffce3009a0fac6be58%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20favorite%20iceberg.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Gail%20Abrams%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20first%20full%20day%2C%20after%20getting%20fitted%20for%20muck%20boots%20and%20waterproof%20polar%20expedition%20jackets%2C%20we%20climbed%20into%20Zodiacs%20and%20set%20out%20to%20explore%20the%20glaciers%2C%20icebergs%2C%20and%20bird%20cliffs.%20At%20times%2C%20it%20looked%20like%20we%20were%20on%20another%20planet%2C%20with%20no%20other%20humans%20in%20sight.%20The%20vast%20expanse%20of%20the%20Arctic%20waters%2C%20the%20exquisite%20ice%20formations%2C%20and%20the%20distant%20glaciers%20were%20overwhelmingly%20beautiful.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOther%20than%20the%20sounds%20of%20the%20Zodiacs%20cutting%20through%20the%20water%20and%20ice%2C%20the%20cawing%20of%20birds%2C%20or%20the%20calving%20of%20the%20icebergs%2C%20we%20were%20silent%20most%20of%20the%20time.%20Our%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-small-ship-cruise-lindblad-expeditions-national-geographic-review-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eexpert%20guides%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20offered%20commentary%20about%20the%20geology%20and%20wildlife%20in%20each%20area%2C%20but%20mostly%2C%20we%20were%20content%20to%20bask%20in%20the%20meditative%20quiet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20saw%20walruses%20sunning%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222572%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Walruses%20on%20ice%20in%20the%20Arctic%20Circle.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e97c62ce3009a0fac6be63%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221929%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThey%20saw%20wildlife%20like%20walruses%20and%20polar%20bears.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Gail%20Abrams%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EArctic%20wildlife%20includes%20such%20wonders%20as%20reindeer%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwildlife-photography-award-napping-polar-bear-natural-history-museum-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epolar%20bears%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20seals%2C%20walruses%2C%20arctic%20foxes%2C%20and%20several%20species%20of%20birds.%20The%20first%20day's%20excitement%20of%20tracking%20a%20reindeer%20across%20a%20mountain%20through%20photos%20and%20video%20was%20only%20exceeded%20by%20the%20polar%20bear%20we%20saw%20on%20the%20second%20day.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20fun%20to%20watch%20the%20polar%20bear%20stalking%20a%20herd%20of%20walruses%20bobbing%20up%20and%20down%20in%20the%20water.%20The%20polar%20bear%20lumbered%20slowly%20toward%20the%20walruses%20and%20then%20stood%20up%20on%20its%20hind%20legs%20and%20actually%20did%20a%20little%20prancing%20jump%20a%20couple%20of%20times.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20silently%20watched%20polar%20bears%20so%20as%20not%20to%20disturb%20them%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Polar%20bear%20walking%20on%20rocks%20near%20water.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e97cb6cfb7f307e572352c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPolar%20bears%20were%20also%20frequent%20sights.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Gail%20Abrams%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlmost%20every%20day%2C%20there%20was%20a%20polar%20bear%20sighting%20either%20from%20the%20ship%20or%20from%20the%20Zodiacs%2C%20and%20each%20time%20was%20more%20thrilling%20than%20the%20last.%20The%20most%20momentous%20was%20when%20we%20did%20a%20%26quot%3Bround%20robin%26quot%3B%20close%20to%20a%20large%20area%20of%20pack%20ice%20upon%20which%20a%20polar%20bear%20was%20sunning.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20circled%20silently%20around%20for%20nearly%20an%20hour%20so%20each%20Zodiac%20could%20get%20closer%20for%20photos%2C%20moving%20slowly%20so%20as%20not%20to%20startle%20the%20bear%20away.%20The%20gentle%20lapping%20of%20the%20water%20against%20the%20sides%20of%20our%20boats%2C%20the%20warm%20sun%20shining%20down%2C%20the%20crisp%20air%2C%20and%20the%20vast%20expanse%20of%20ice%20and%20snow%20was%20hypnotic.%20Time%20was%20suspended%2C%20and%20we%20were%20content.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20got%20to%20make%20a%20rare%20visit%20to%20Kvit%C3%B8ya%2C%20or%20White%20Island%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20at%20a%20monument%20on%20White%20Island.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e97d7fcfb7f307e5723543%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20at%20the%20monument%20on%20White%20Island.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Gail%20Abrams%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20highlight%20was%20our%20rare%20excursion%20to%20Kvit%C3%B8ya%2C%20the%20White%20Island.%20From%20the%20ship%2C%20it%20looks%20like%20a%20wide%20white%20dome%20floating%20in%20the%20water%2C%20with%20no%20vegetation%20interrupting%20the%20smooth%20and%20nearly%20blinding%20expanse%20of%20snow.%20It%20was%20the%20landing%20site%20of%20a%20three-man%20expedition%20crew%20led%20by%20Swedish%20explorer%20S.A.%20Andree%20in%201897.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feric-larsen-and-ryan-waters-north-pole-expedition-may-be-the-last-2016-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESearching%20for%20the%20North%20Pole%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20a%20hydrogen%20balloon%20that%20had%20not%20been%20properly%20tested%2C%20they%20crashed%20only%20three%20days%20after%20launch.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETheir%20whereabouts%20were%20unknown%20until%201930%2C%20when%20the%20remains%20were%20discovered%20by%20another%20expedition%20team%20who%20found%20diaries%2C%20scientific%20logs%2C%20and%20glass%20negative%20plates%20from%20which%20photographs%20could%20be%20developed.%20It%20was%20deduced%20that%20Andree%20and%20his%20fellow%20explorers%20died%20within%20two%20weeks%20of%20landing%20on%20Kvit%C3%B8ya.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20experienced%20a%20once-in-a-lifetime%20hike%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22View%20of%20an%20expeditioner's%20hut%20across%20water%20with%20mountains%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e97e03d17aa3c7b2b34334%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20saw%20an%20expeditioner's%20hut%20across%20an%20expanse%20of%20water.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Gail%20Abrams%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20our%20expedition%20leader%20Howard%20Whelan%2C%20who%20has%20worked%20for%20Aurora%20for%2022%20years%2C%20Zodiacs%20have%20been%20able%20to%20approach%20%3C%2Fspan%3EKvit%C3%B8ya%3Cspan%3E%20but%20not%20land%20on%20the%20island.%20Either%20the%20water%20is%20too%20choppy%2C%20or%20the%20weather%20conditions%20are%20too%20windy%20or%20foggy.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20this%20particular%20day%2C%20the%20weather%20was%20pristine%2C%20and%20we%20were%20the%20first%20group%20that%20Howard%20has%20been%20able%20to%20safely%20land%20on%20the%20island%20to%20trek%20up%20to%20the%20monument%20honoring%20the%20three%20explorers.%20Starting%20next%20year%2C%20the%20Arctic%20Circle%20will%20be%20restricted%20to%20only%2043%20sites%20where%20people%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20land%2C%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3EKvit%C3%B8ya%3Cspan%3E%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20accessible%20in%20the%20same%20way.%20So%20we%20were%20very%20fortunate%20to%20experience%20this%20once-in-a-lifetime%20hike.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20didn't%20see%20the%20northern%20lights%20and%20had%20to%20%26quot%3Bcreate%26quot%3B%20nighttime%20in%20our%20rooms%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20%26quot%3BLion's%20Head%26quot%3B%20iceberg%20in%20the%20forefront%20with%20a%20Zodiac%20of%20people%20behind%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e97e85cfb7f307e572355f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20and%20her%20sister%20saw%20the%20%26quot%3BLion's%20Head%26quot%3B%20iceberg.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPeople%20have%20asked%20if%20we%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsaw-northern-lights-surprising-photos-misleading-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaw%20the%20northern%20lights%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3B%20unfortunately%2C%20summer%20is%20not%20the%20time%20of%20year%20to%20witness%20that%20phenomenon.%20Instead%2C%20we%20had%2024%20hours%20of%20daylight%2C%20which%20was%20truly%20a%20weird%20experience.%20It%20was%20just%20as%20bright%20and%20sunny%20at%2010%20p.m.%20as%20at%208%20a.m.%2C%20and%20we%20had%20to%20%26quot%3Bcreate%26quot%3B%20nighttime%20by%20closing%20the%20blackout%20curtains%20in%20our%20stateroom%20to%20sleep.%20Our%20circadian%20rhythms%20were%20out%20of%20whack%2C%20but%20after%20a%20few%20days%2C%20we%20adjusted%20fairly%20well.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20crew%20was%20incredible.%20They%20were%20knowledgeable%20about%20the%20history%20and%20science%20of%20this%20remarkable%20area%20and%20well-trained%20in%20safety%20measures%20on%20land%20and%20water.%20They%20ate%20with%20and%20circulated%20amongst%20the%20passengers%2C%20and%20they%20were%20attentive%20to%20diverse%20physical%20capabilities%20by%20offering%20varying%20levels%20of%20exertion%20on%20hikes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20ship%20was%20homey%2C%20and%20I%20loved%20the%20experience%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Zodiacs%20in%20ice%20in%20the%20Arctic%20Circle.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e97f0bd17aa3c7b2b34349%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EExpert%20guides%20took%20them%20out%20in%20Zodiacs%20to%20explore%20glaciers%20and%20icebergs.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Gail%20Abrams%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ship%20is%20small%2C%20homey%2C%20and%20friendly.%20The%20food%20was%20plentiful%20and%20excellent%2C%20and%20attention%20to%20individual%20dietary%20needs%20and%20preferences%20was%20stellar.%20Beer%20and%20house%20wine%2C%20as%20well%20as%20soft%20drinks%20and%20juices%2C%20are%20included%20with%20dinner%2C%20and%20there%20are%20always%20snacks%2C%20coffee%2C%20and%20tea%20available.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20medical%20clinic%20and%20doctor%20on%20board%2C%20with%20medications%20available%20if%20needed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspa