ns-gen-z-millennials-recommend-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%20asked%20young%20professionals%20on%20the%20street%20to%20name%20the%20best%20travel%20destination%20that%20might%20fly%20under%20most%20people's%20radars.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mnoyen%40insider.com%20(Maria%20Noyen%2CMykenna%20Maniece)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhidden-gem-travel-destinations-gen-z-millennials-recommend-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Announces%2050%20Quad%20Scholarships%20Worth%20Rs%204%20Crore%2C%20Check%20Details%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3EIndia%20has%20launched%20a%20new%20initiative%20to%20offer%20fifty%20Quad%20scholarships%2C%20valued%20at%20%24500%2C000%20(around%20Rs%204%2C17%2C40%2C225)%2C%20to%20students%20from%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region.%20These%20scholarships%20will%20support%20students%20pursuing%20a%204-year%20undergraduate%20engineering%20program%20at%20a%20Government%20of%20India-funded%20technical%20institution.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20announcement%20follows%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20participation%20in%20the%20Quad%20Summit%20in%20Wilmington%2C%20Delaware.%20The%20meeting%20was%20attended%20by%20U.S.%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Anthony%20Albanese%20of%20Australia%2C%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Fumio%20Kishida%20of%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fellowship%20will%20be%20managed%20by%20the%20Institute%20of%20International%20Education%20(IIE)%2C%20a%20global%20not-for-profit%20organization.%20Starting%20in%202024%2C%20the%20fellowship%20will%20also%20sponsor%20master's%20and%20doctoral%20students%20to%20study%20science%2C%20technology%2C%20engineering%2C%20and%20mathematics%20(STEM)%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20website%20reads%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20fellowship%20develops%20a%20network%20of%20science%20and%20technology%20experts%20committed%20to%20advancing%20innovation%20and%20collaboration%20in%20the%20private%2C%20public%2C%20and%20academic%20sectors%2C%20in%20their%20own%20nations%20and%20among%20Quad%20countries.%20The%20program%20builds%20foundational%20understanding%20among%20Quad%20Fellows%20of%20one%20another's%20societies%20and%20cultures%20through%20programming%20and%20networking%20opportunities%20with%20each%20country's%20top%20scientists%2C%20technologists%2C%20and%20politicians.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEligibility%20For%20Master's%20And%20Doctoral%20Programs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECandidates%20must%20be%20at%20least%2018%20years%20old%20at%20the%20time%20of%20application%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EApplicants%20must%20be%20citizens%20or%20legal%20permanent%20residents%20of%20one%20of%20the%20Quad%20countries-Australia%2C%20India%2C%20Japan%2C%20or%20the%20United%20States-or%20any%20of%20the%20Southeast%20Asian%20countries%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStudents%20must%20have%20completed%20a%20bachelor's%20degree%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinancial%20Benefits%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEach%20Quad%20Fellow%20will%20receive%20a%20one-time%20financial%20grant%20of%20%2440%2C000%20(Rs%2033%2C39%2C218)%20to%20cover%20academic%20expenses.%20However%2C%20the%20detailed%20eligibility%20criteria%20have%20not%20yet%20been%20announced%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Quad%20is%20a%20diplomatic%20partnership%20between%20Australia%2C%20India%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727000580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F33b0679o_esfsr_625x300_22_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Findia-announces-50-quad-scholarships-worth-rs-4-crore-check-details-6623555%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20fellowship%20will%20be%20managed%20by%20the%2