rder%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113570246.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EA%20century-old%20artillery%20round%20weighing%20nearly%20300%20kilogrammes%20(660%20pounds)%2C%20was%20safely%20removed%20on%20Sunday%20from%20a%20construction%20site%20near%20the%20Serbian%20Parliament%20in%20Belgrade%2C%20police%20said.%20In%20Nis%2C%20southern%20Serbia%2C%20a%20large%20bomb%20from%20the%201999%20NATO%20bombing%20was%20discovered%20in%20April%2C%20while%20in%202021%2C%20a%20242-kilogramme%20bomb%20from%20WWII%20was%20removed%20from%20a%20construction%20site%20in%20a%20Belgrade%20suburb.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2F300-kilo-wwi-bomb-removed-in-belgrade%2Farticleshow%2F113570246.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2F300-kilo-wwi-bomb-removed-in-belgrade%2Famp_articleshow%2F113570246.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2F300-kilo-wwi-bomb-removed-in-belgrade%2Famp_articleshow%2F113570246.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BChandrababu%20Naidu%20Habitual%20Liar%26quot%3B%3A%20Jagan%20Reddy%20Writes%20To%20PM%20Amid%20Laddoo%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20massive%20row%20over%20allegations%20that%20animal%20fat%20was%20used%20in%20the%20preparation%20of%20Tirupati%20laddus%2C%20former%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20YS%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20has%20written%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20calling%20the%20incumbent%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Chandrababu%20a%20%26quot%3Bpathological%20liar%26quot%3B%20and%20accusing%20him%20hurting%20the%20beliefs%20of%20crores%20of%20people%20%26quot%3Bpurely%20for%20political%20objectives%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20YSR%20Congress%20Party%20chief%20has%20said%20the%20entire%20country%20is%20looking%20at%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20it%20is%20imperative%20that%20Mr%20Naidu%20%26quot%3Bbe%20reprimanded%20in%20(the)%20severest%20way%20for%20his%20shameless%20act%20of%20spreading%20lies%26quot%3B.%20He%20has%20demanded%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Btruth%20be%20brought%20to%20light%26quot%3B%20to%20allay%20the%20suspicions%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20crores%20of%20Hindu%20devotees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Naidu's%20TDP%20swept%20the%20Andhra%20polls%20this%20year%20and%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20Mr%20Reddy's%20exit%20as%20Chief%20Minister.%20TDP%20is%20also%20a%20key%20ally%20of%20the%20BJP%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20its%20support%20is%20critical%20to%20NDA's%20majority%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20after%20the%20BJP%20suffered%20a%20setback%20in%20this%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Reddy%20has%20accused%20Mr%20Naidu%20of%20trying%20to%20%26quot%3Birreparably%20tarnish%20the%20sanctity%2C%20integrity%20and%20reputation%20of%20Tirumala%20Tirupati%20Devasthanams%26quot%3B%20and%20warned%20that%20this%20could%20have%20far-reaching%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20YSRCP%20chief%20claimed%20that%20the%20people's%20perception%20of%20the%20new%20government%20is%20%26quot%3Bquite%20negative%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20Tirupati%20row%20was%20aimed%20at%20diverting%20attention%20from%20its%20failures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20an%20NDA%20legislative%20party%20meeting%20Wednesday%2C%20Mr%20Naidu%20said%20animal%20fat%20was%20used%20to%20make%20the%20sought-after%20laddoos%20given%20as%20'prasad'%20by%20the%20Sri%20Venkateswara%20Temple%20under%20the%20Jagan%20Reddy%20government.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Reddy%20said%20the%20tanker%20containing%20the%20possibly%20adulterated%20ghee%20arrived%20at%20Tirupati%20on%20July%2012%2C%20but%20was%20rejected%20and%20not%20used%20to%20prepare%20prasadams.%20%26quot%3BThe%20robust%20practices%20in%20place%20for%20decades%20in%20TTD%20could%20identify%20the%20questionable%20quality%20and%20therefore%20the%20ghee%20was%20not%20used.%20Despite%20this%20comforting%20scenario%2C%20Mr.%20Naidu%20chose%20to%20callously%20make%20a%20remark%20that%20Tirumala%20Laddus%20were%20made%20with%20animal%20fats%20and%20not%20with%20ghee%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20stressed%20the%20robustness%20of%20the%20policies%20and%20procedures%20of%20Tirumala%20Tirupati%20Devasthanams%2C%20which%20manages%20the%20temple.%20Explaining%20the%20checks%20to%20ensure%20the%20ghee's%20quality%2C%20he%20said%20every%20tanker%20that%20reaches%20the%20temple%20should%20have%20certification%20on%20the%20purity%20of%20ghee%20from%20agencies%20accredited%20by%20NABL%20--%20National%20Accreditation%20Board%20for%20Testing%20and%20Calibration%20Laboratories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFurther%20at%20the%20temple%2C%20three%20samples%20are%20obtained%20from%20every%20tanker%20and%20the%20same%20are%20tested%20and%20only%20after%20the%20three%20samples%20pass%20the%20test%20would%20the%20ghee%20be%20allowed%20to%20be%20put%20to%20use.%20If%20it%20so%20happens%20that%20if%20even%20one%20of%20the%20samples%20turns%20out%20to%20be%20substandard%2C%20the%20tanker%20is%20rejected%20and%20is%20not%20allowed%20to%20pass.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20question%20of%20sub-standard%20material%20being%20used%20in%20the%20preparation%20of%20prasadams%20does%20not%20arise%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Reddy%20said.%20He%20added%20that%20this%20process%20has%20been%20in%20force%20for%20several%20decades%20and%20there%20have%20been%20several%20instances%20when%20tankers%20were%20rejected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20responsible%20Chief%20Minister%20should%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20attempt%20to%20bring%20to%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20public%20the%20robustness%20of%20the%20checks%20and%20balances%20in%20place%20to%20give%20them%20comfort%20as%20to%20sanctity%20of%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20TTD.%20The%20way%20in%20which%20Mr%20Naidu%20acted%20was%20in%20a%20manner%20totally%20devoid%20of%20social%20responsibility%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alleged%20report%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20said%2C%20contains%20some%20very%20serious%20disclaimers.%20%26quot%3BThe%20report%20conveys%20that%20the%20finding%20would%20not%20be%20applicable%20if%20the%20milk%20fat%20belongs%20to%20various%20categories%20that%20are%20listed%20out%20in%20the%20annexure.%20The%20categories%20include%20scenarios%20such%20as%20milk%20fat%20being%20obtained%20from%20cows%20which%20received%20an%20exceptionally%20high%20feeding%20of%20pure%20vegetable%20oils%2C%20cotton%20or%20palm%20oils%2C%20milk%20fat%20obtained%20from%20cows%20that%20are%20suffering%20from%20energy%20deficiency%2C%20milk%20fat%20obtained%20from%20cheeses.%20showing%20increased%20lipolysis%20and%20so%20forth.%20Therefore%2C%20if%20any%20of%20the%20above%20scenarios%20exist%2C%20then%20the%20methodology%20adopted%20would%20yield%20an%20incorrect%20or%20false%20positive%20result.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20YSRCP%20leader%20said%20Mr%20Naidu%20had%2C%20in%20%26quot%3Btotal%20disregard%20to%20strong%20religious%20sentiments%20and%20with%20the%20malafide%20intent%20to%20spread%20lies%26quot%3B%2C%20brought%20the%20issue%20to%20light%20in%20a%20political%20party%20meeting%20on%20September%2018%2C%20more%20than%20two%20months%20after%20the%20tanker%20was%20rejected.%20%26quot%3BThe%20inaction%20of%20Mr.%20Naidu%20for%20the%20period%20of%20two%20months%20conveys%20that%20he%20did%20not%20believe%20that%20the%20ghee%20was%20adulterated%20physically%20with%20animal%20fats%20and%20that%20the%20finding%20of%20questionable%20quality%20was%20made%20in%20the%20process%20of%20routine%20checks%20as%20per%20the%20protocol.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSir%2C%20Mr.%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20a%20pathological%20and%20habitual%20liar%20has%20stooped%20so%20low%20as%20to%20seriously%20hurt%20the%20beliefs%20of%20crores%20of%20people%20purely%20for%20political%20objectives.%20His%20actions%20have%20indeed%20lowered%20not%20only%20the%20stature%20of%20a%20Chief%20Minister%20but%20also%20that%20of%20everyone%20in%20public%20life%20and%20also%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20world%20renowned%20TTD%20and%20its%20practices.%20Sir%2C%20the%20entire%20Country%20looks%20to%20you%20at%20this%20crucial%20juncture.%20It%20is%20very%20imperative%20that%20Mr.%20Naidu%20be%20reprimanded%20in%20severest%20way%20for%20his%20shameless%20act%20of%20spreading%20lies%20and%20the%20truth%20be%20brought%20to%20light%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSir%2C%20this%20would%20help%20allay%20the%20suspicions%20that%20Mr.%20Naidu%20has%20created%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20crores%20of%20hindu%20devotees%20and%20restore%20their%20faith%20in%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20TTD%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Reddy%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727000040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fubpmh698_jagan-reddy-chandrababu-naidu_625x300_07_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-jagan-mohan-reddy-n-chandrababu-naidu-chandrababu-naidu-habitual-liar-jagan-reddy-writes-to-pm-amid-laddoo-row-6623496%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20massive%20row%20over%20allegations%20that%20animal%20fat%20was%20used%20in%20the%20preparation%20of%20Tirupati%20laddus%2C%20former%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20YS%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20has%20written%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-jagan-mohan-reddy-n-chandrababu-naidu-chandrababu-naidu-habitual-liar-jagan-reddy-writes-to-pm-amid-laddoo-row-6623496%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Top%2010%20goal%20scorers%20in%20EPL%20history%3A%20Shearer%2C%20Kane%2C%20Rooney%20and%20more%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%2