0in%20India%20by%20Zee%20Studios%20in%20collaboration%20with%20'Zindagi'%2C%20which%20also%20featured%20Fawad%20Khan%20in%20its%20show%20'Barzakh'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNavratri%20festival%20will%20start%20around%20the%20time%20when%20this%20movie%20will%20be%20released.%20I%20do%20not%20want%20any%20conflict%20to%20happen%20in%20Maharashtra.%20And%20the%20same%20will%20not%20be%20the%20wish%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20the%20state%2C%20the%20Home%20Minister%20and%20the%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20of%20the%20state.%20And%20we%20don't%20want%20any%20conflict%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Thackeray%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wish%20that%20there%20should%20be%20no%20conflict%20in%20the%20state%20for%20any%20Pakistani%20cinema%20and%20I%20am%20sure%20that%20the%20government%20will%20give%20due%20attention%20to%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E'The%20Legend%20of%20Maula%20Jatt'%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewould%20be%20the%20first%20Pakistani%20movie%20to%20release%20in%20India%20since%202011's%20'%3Cem%3EBol%3C%2Fem%3E'%2C%20starring%20Humaima%20Malick%20and%20Atif%20Aslam.%20Its%20release%20was%20initially%20planned%20for%20December%202022%20but%20faced%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ban%20on%20Pakistani%20artists%20working%20in%20India%20was%20implemented%20after%20the%202016%20Uri%20terror%20attack%2C%20which%20led%20to%20tensions%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20and%20disrupted%20cultural%20exchanges%2C%20including%20Fawad%20Khan's%20flourishing%20career%20in%20Bollywood.%20Although%20Fawad%20and%20Mahira%20remain%20popular%20in%20India%2C%20the%20political%20climate%20continues%20to%20complicate%20their%20involvement%20in%20Indian%20cinema.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726992660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F9r37f9ug_raj-thackeray-fawad-khan-_625x300_22_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fahead-of-fawad-khans-film-relea