-old%20boy%20was%20allegedly%20sexually%20harassed%20by%20his%20chemistry%20teacher%20at%20a%20private%20school%20in%20Bhopal.%20The%20teacher%20reportedly%20threatened%20the%20student%20with%20failing%20grades%20and%20recorded%20inappropriate%20videos.%20The%20situation%20came%20to%20light%20when%20the%20boy's%20class%20teacher%20spoke%20to%20him%20after%20he%20received%20low%20marks%20in%20an%20examination.%20The%20school%20principal%20was%20then%20informed%2C%20leading%20to%20police%20involvement.%20An%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20the%20teacher%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20and%20presented%20in%20court%2C%20where%20he%20was%20remanded%20to%20judicial%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20incident%20on%20Saturday%2C%20a%205-year-old%20girl%20reported%20being%20sexually%20abused%20by%20her%20school%20van%20driver.%20The%20child%20returned%20home%20crying%20and%20informed%20her%20mother%20about%20the%20incident.%20But%20when%20enquired%20at%20the%20police%20station%2C%20she%20did%20not%20mention%20the%20details%20prompting%20the%20Child%20Welfare%20Committee%20(CWC)%20to%20schedule%20a%20counselling%20with%20her%20today%20to%20gather%20more%20information.%20As%20of%20now%2C%20the%20police%20have%20detained%20the%20driver%20for%20questioning%2C%20but%20no%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20him%20yet.%20However%2C%20Bhopal%20Police%20Commissioner%20Harinarayanachari%20Mishra%20has%20confirmed%20that%20the%20case%20is%20being%20taken%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20days%20ago%2C%20a%203-year-old%20girl%20was%20sexually%20abused%20by%20her%20IT%20teacher%20at%20a%20different%20private%20school.%20Her%20mother%20noticed%20suspicious%20scratches%20on%20her%20body%2C%20which%20she%20initially%20thought%20to%20be%20accidental.%20After%20questioning%20the%20child%2C%20who%20referred%20to%20the%20perpetrator%20as%20%26quot%3Buncle%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20mother%20reported%20the%20matter%20to%20authorities.%20Following%20a%20medical%20examin