king%20as%20a%20techie%20at%20a%20software%20firm%20for%20the%20past%2015%20years.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fchennai%2Ftragic-work-related-suicide-software-engineer-electrocutes-himself-in-chennai%2Farticleshow%2F113532275.cms%5C%22%3EPolice%20have%20said%20Karthikeyan%20had%20earlier%20complained%20of%20being%20upset%20due%20to%20work%20pressure%20and%20was%20under%20treatment%20for%20depression%20for%20two%20months%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20The%20Times%20of%20India.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarthikeyan%20was%20alone%20at%20home%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident.%20His%20wife%20K%20Jayarani%20left%20for%20Thirunallur%20temple%2C%20about%20300%20km%20from%20Chennai%2C%20on%20Monday.%20She%20dropped%20off%20the%20children%20at%20her%20mother's%20place.%20She%20returned%20on%20Thursday%20night%20and%20knocked%2C%20but%20there%20was%20no%20response.%20She%20used%20a%20spare%20key%20to%20enter%20the%20house%20and%20found%20Karthikeyan%20lying%20with%20a%20live%20wire%20wrapped%20around%20his%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20case%20of%20unnatural%20death%20has%20been%20registered%20and%20a%20probe%20is%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20techie's%20death%20by%20suicide%2C%20allegedly%20due%20to%20depression%20over%20work%20pressure%2C%20has%20taken%20place%20amid%20nationwide%20outrage%20over%20toxic%20work%20conditions%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20death%20of%20a%2026-year-old%20chartered%20accountant%20with%20Ernst%20%26amp%3B%20Young.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Labour%20Ministry%20has%20launched%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20death%20of%20Anna%20Sebastian%20Perayil%20after%20her%20mother%20alleged%20that%20a%20work%20culture%20that%20%26quot%3Bseems%20to%20glorify%20overwork%26quot%3B%20affected%20her%20health%2C%20eventually%20leading%20to%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnita%20Augustine%20wrote%20to%20Ersnt%20%26amp%3B%20Young%20India%20chairman%20Rajiv%20Memani%20that%20Anna%20worked%20late%20into%20the%20night%2C%20even%20on%20weekends%2C%20%26quot%3Bwith%20no%20opportunity%20to%20catch%20her%20breath%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BHer%20assistant%20manager%20once%20called%20her%20at%20night%20with%20a%20task%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20completed%20by%20the%20next%20morning%2C%20leaving%20her%20with%20barely%20any%20time%20to%20rest%20or%20recover.%20When%20she%20voiced%20her%20concerns%2C%20she%20was%20met%20with%20the%20dismissive%20response%2C%20'You%20can%20work%20at%20night%2C%20that's%20what%20we%20all%20do'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnna%20would%20return%20to%20her%20room%20utterly%20exhausted%2C%20sometimes%20collapsing%20on%20the%20bed%20without%20even%20changing%20her%20clothes%2C%20only%20to%20be%20bombarded%20with%20messages%20asking%20for%20more%20reports.%20She%20was%20putting%20in%20her%20best%20efforts%2C%20working%20very%20hard%20to%20meet%20the%20deadlines.%20She%20was%20a%20fighter%20to%20the%20core%2C%20not%20someone%20to%20give%20up%20easily.%20We%20told%20her%20to%20quit%2C%20but%20she%20wanted%20to%20learn%20and%20gain%20new%20exposure.%20However%2C%20the%20overwhelming%20pressure%20proved%20too%20much%20even%20for%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Memani%20has%20said%20that%20Ernst%20%26amp%3B%20Young%20places%20the%20highest%20importance%20on%20the%20well%20being%20of%20its%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20posted%20on%20LinkedIn%20on%20Thursday%20night%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20deeply%20saddened%20and%20as%20a%20father%2C%20I%20can%20only%20imagine%20Ms%20Augustine's%20grief.%20I%20have%20conveyed%20my%20deepest%20condolences%20to%20the%20family%2C%20although%20nothing%20can%20fill%20the%20void%20in%20their%20lives.%20I%20truly%20regret%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20missed%20being%20present%20at%20Anna's%20funeral.%20This%20is%20completely%20alien%20to%20our%20culture.%20It%20has%20never%20happened%20before%3B%20it%20will%20never%20happen%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3