r-apple-products-following-iphone-16-launch-6621838%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Days%20after%20Apple%20launched%20its%20highly%20anticipated%20iPhone%2016%20series%2C%20the%20Indian%20Computer%20Emergency%20Response%20Team%20(CERT-In)%20has%20issued%20a%20high-risk%20warning%20concerning%20multiple%20vulnerabilities%20found%20in%20several%20Apple%20products.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcert-issues-high-risk-warning-for-iphones-other-apple-products-following-iphone-16-launch-6621838%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Global%20trends%2C%20foreign%20investors%20key%20drivers%20for%20markets%20this%20week%3A%20Experts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726982612000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-09%2F20%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1726822818-4636.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fglobal-trends-foreign-investors-key-drivers-for-markets-this-week-experts-124092200135_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stock%20markets%20had%20a%20record-breaking%20rally%20last%20week%2C%20largely%20driven%20by%20the%20US%20Federal%20Reserve's%20rate%20cut%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fglobal-trends-foreign-investors-key-drivers-for-markets-this-week-experts-124092200135_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fglobal-trends-foreign-investors-key-drivers-for-markets-this-week-experts-124092200135_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fglobal-trends-foreign-investors-key-drivers-for-markets-this-week-experts-124092200135_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Human%20Rights%20Body%20Seeks%20Centre's%20Response%20On%20EY%20Employee's%20Death%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20(NHRC)%20has%20sought%20a%20detailed%20response%20from%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Labour%20and%20Employment%20over%20the%20death%20of%20a%20young%20chartered%20accountant%20in%20Pune.%20Anna%20Sebastian%20Perayil%2C%20a%2026-year-old%20employee%20at%20Ernst%20%26amp%3B%20Young%20(EY)%2C%20died%20in%20July%202024%2C%20allegedly%20due%20to%20excessive%20workload%20and%20intense%20work%20pressure%2C%20according%20to%20her%20family.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20issued%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20NHRC%20expressed%20grave%20concern%20over%20the%20circumstances%20surrounding%20Ms%20Perayil's%20death.%20It%20called%20on%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Labour%20and%20Employment%20to%20provide%20a%20comprehensive%20report%20on%20the%20case%2C%20including%20details%20of%20the%20ongoing%20investigation.%20Union%20Labour%20Minister%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%20confirmed%20that%20the%20ministry%20is%20looking%20into%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20NHRC%2C%20the%20reports%20surrounding%20Ms%20Perayil's%20death%20raise%20serious%20concerns%20about%20the%20mental%20and%20physical%20toll%20of%20corporate%20work%20culture%20on%20young%20employees%2C%20particularly%20those%20in%20high-pressure%20industries%20like%20finance%2C%20consulting%2C%20and%20law.%20Stress%2C%20anxiety%2C%20sleeplessness%2C%20and%20the%20relentless%20pursuit%20of%20impossible%20targets%20have%2C%20the%20NHRC%20noted%2C%20led%20to%20%26quot%3Bgrave%20violations%20of%20their%20human%20rights.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20growing%20concerns%20around%20workplace%20safety%2C%20the%20NHRC%20has%20constituted%20a%20'Core%20Group%20on%20Business%20and%20Human%20Rights.'%20This%20body%20will%20review%20current%20labour%20legislations%20and%20regulations%2C%20aiming%20to%20create%20robust%20recommendations%20for%20both%20central%20and%20state%20governments.%20The%20core%20group's%20objective%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20businesses%20in%20India%20align%20their%20practices%20with%20global%20human%20rights%20standards%20and%20create%20healthy%2C%20humane%20work%20environments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20employer%20has%20a%20prime%20duty%20to%20provide%20a%20safe%2C%20secure%2C%20and%20positive%20environment%20for%20its%20employees.%20It%20is%20vital%20that%20businesses%20regularly%20update%20and%20revise%20their%20employment%20policies%20to%20reflect%20their%20commitment%20to%20human%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20NHRC's%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20of%20Ms%20Perayil%2C%20who%20had%20been%20working%20at%20EY's%20Pune%20office%20for%20only%20four%20months%2C%20has%20drawn%20attention%20to%20corporate%20work%20culture.%20Her%20mother's%20emotional%20letter%20to%20the%20company%2C%20which%20has%20since%20gone%20viral%2C%20accused%20the%20firm%20of%20creating%20an%20unbearable%20working%20environment%20that%20led%20to%20her%20daughter's%20death.%20In%20her%20letter%2C%20she%20pointed%20out%20the%20long%20hours%2C%20intense%20pressure%2C%20and%20the%20prioritisation%20of%20work%20over%20employee%20well-being%20as%20factors%20that%20caused%20her%20daughter's%20deteriorating%20mental%20and%20physical%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Perayil%20reportedly%20died%20of%20cardiac%20arrest%2C%20but%20her%20family%20claims%20that%20the%20extreme%20workload%20and%20stressful%20work%20environment%20were%20the%20real%20cause.%20Her%20father%2C%20Sibi%20Joseph%2C%20spoke%20out%20about%20the%20unbearable%20pressure%20his%20daughter%20was%20under.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20used%20to%20cry%20on%20the%20phone%20that%20she%20could%20not%20work%20with%20so%20much%20tension%20and%20stress.%20We%20asked%20her%20to%20resign%20and%20come%20back...%20She%20decided%20to%20continue%20because%20she%20said%20that%20she%20was%20getting%20more%20exposure%20in%20EY.%20Unfortunately%2C%20on%20July%2021%2C%20she%20collapsed%20in%20her%20room%20and%20died%20before%20reaching%20the%20hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Joseph%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20claims%2C%20EY%20has%20denied%20any%20wrongdoing.%20In%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20company%20expressed%20deep%20sorrow%20over%20Ms%20Perayil's%20death%2C%20noting%20that%20it%20had%20been%20in%20contact%20with%20the%20family%20and%20had%20offered%20support.%20The%20firm%20also%20addressed%20the%20accusations%20of%20excessive%20workload%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20deeply%20saddened%20by%20Anna%20Sebastian's%20tragic%20and%20untimely%20passing%20in%20July%202024.%20We%20place%20the%20highest%20importance%20on%20the%20well-being%20of%20all%20employees%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20improve%20and%20provide%20a%20healthy%20workplace.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20also%20come%20under%20fire%20for%20allegedly%20failing%20to%20attend%20Perayil's%20funeral%2C%20a%20point%20highlighted%20by%20her%20grieving%20mother.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726982220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F3ulfb94o_anna-sebastian_625x300_19_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhuman-rights-body-seeks-centres-response-on-ey-employees-death-6621904%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20(NHRC)%20has%20sought%20a%20detailed%20response%20from%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Labour%20and%20Employment%20over%20the%20death%20of%20a%20young%20chartered%20accountant%20in%20Pune.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhuman-rights-body-seeks-centres-response-on-ey-employees-death-6621904%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22At%20least%2019%20killed%20in%20coal%20mine%20blast%20in%20Iran's%20Tabas%2