mpaign%20highlighted%20his%20participation%20in%20two%20debates%20compared%20to%20Harris'%20one%2C%20suggesting%20the%20timing%20is%20not%20appropriate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-says-too-late-after-harris-accepts-another-debate-proposal%2Farticleshow%2F113563803.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-says-too-late-after-harris-accepts-another-debate-proposal%2Famp_articleshow%2F113563803.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-says-too-late-after-harris-accepts-another-debate-proposal%2Famp_articleshow%2F113563803.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Security%20Council%20To%20Space%20Tech%3A%20Key%20Takeaways%20From%20Modi-Biden%20Meet%20In%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20commended%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20for%20his%20historic%20visit%20to%20Ukraine%20and%20his%20message%20of%20peace%20amid%20the%20war%20with%20Russia.%20The%20US%20also%20backed%20permanent%20membership%20for%20India%20in%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20Are%20Some%20Of%20The%20Key%20Takeaways%20From%20The%20Bilateral%20Meet%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Feach-time-we-sit-down-biden-posts-pics-of-meeting-pm-modi-6619870%5C%22%3EREAD%3A%20%26quot%3BEach%20Time%20We%20Sit%20Down...%26quot%3B%3A%20Biden%20Posts%20Pics%20Of%20Meeting%20PM%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBoost%20For%20India-US%20Ties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20met%20the%20US%20president%20at%20his%20home%20in%20Wilmington%2C%20North%20Carolina.%20At%20the%20meeting%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20conveyed%20his%20appreciation%20for%20President%20Biden's%20unparalleled%20contributions%20in%20giving%20impetus%20to%20the%20India-US%20partnership%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20said.%20Recalling%20his%20earlier%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20last%20year%20and%20President%20Biden's%20India%20trip%20for%20the%20G20%20summit%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20noted%20that%20visits%20have%20led%20to%20greater%20dynamism%20and%20depth%20in%20the%20India-US%20partnership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20emphasised%20that%20India%20and%20the%20US%20now%20enjoy%20a%20comprehensive%20global%20strategic%20partnership%20that%20covers%20all%20areas%20of%20human%20endeavour%2C%20driven%20by%20shared%20democratic%20values%2C%20convergence%20of%20interests%20and%20vibrant%20people-to-people%20ties%2C%20the%20MEA%20said.%20It%20added%20that%20the%20two%20leaders%20discussed%20ways%20to%20enhance%20bilateral%20cooperation%20in%20areas%20of%20mutual%20interest%20and%20exchanged%20views%20on%20global%20and%20regional%20issues%2C%20including%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region%20and%20beyond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20Global%20Role%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Biden%20expressed%20appreciation%20for%20India's%20leadership%20on%20the%20world%20stage%2C%20particularly%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20leadership%20in%20the%20G20%20and%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20a%20White%20House%20statement%20said.%20The%20US%20President%20also%20praised%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20commitment%20to%20strengthen%20the%20Quad%20to%20ensure%20a%20free%2C%20open%2C%20and%20prosperous%20Indo-Pacific.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20efforts%20to%20seek%20solutions%20to%20the%20most%20pressing%20challenges%2C%20from%20supporting%20the%20global%20response%20to%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20to%20addressing%20the%20devastating%20consequences%20of%20conflicts%20around%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20White%20House%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Biden%2C%20it%20said%2C%20commended%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20for%20his%20historic%20visits%20to%20Poland%20and%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20first%20by%20an%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20decades%2C%20and%20his%20message%20of%20peace%20and%20ongoing%20humanitarian%20support%20for%20Ukraine.%20The%20statement%20was%20silent%20on%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20visit%20to%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Biden%20told%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20that%20the%20US%20supports%20initiatives%20to%20reform%20global%20institutions%20to%20%26quot%3Breflect%20India's%20important%20voice%26quot%3B.%20The%20US%20also%20backed%20permanent%20membership%20for%20India%20in%20a%20reformed%20UN%20Security%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpace%20To%20Semiconductors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20has%20said%20that%20the%20two%20leaders%20cheered%20the%20success%20of%20the%20Initiative%20on%20Critical%20and%20Emerging%20Technology%20(iCET)%20in%20deepening%20and%20expanding%20strategic%20cooperation%20across%20key%20technology%20sectors%2C%20including%20space%2C%20semiconductors%2C%20and%20advanced%20telecommunications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20Leaders%20committed%20to%20enhance%20regular%20engagements%20to%20improve%20the%20momentum%20of%20collaboration%20in%20fields%20such%20as%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20quantum%2C%20biotechnology%2C%20and%20clean%20energy.%20They%20highlighted%20ongoing%20efforts%20to%20strengthen%20collaboration%20with%20like-minded%20partners%2C%20including%20through%20the%20Quad%20and%20a%20U.S.-India-ROK%20Trilateral%20Technology%20initiative%20launched%20earlier%20this%20year%20to%20build%20more%20secure%20and%20resilient%20supply%20chains%20for%20critical%20industries%20and%20ensure%20we%20collectively%20remain%20at%20the%20leading%20edge%20of%20innovation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%20The%20leaders%2C%20it%20said%2C%20also%20endorsed%20new%20mechanisms%20for%20deeper%20cyberspace%20cooperation%20through%20the%20bilateral%20cybersecurity%20dialogue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Biden%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20hailed%20a%20watershed%20arrangement%20to%20establish%20a%20new%20semiconductor%20fabrication%20plant%20focused%20on%20advanced%20sensing%2C%20communication%2C%20and%20power%20electronics%20for%20national%20security%2C%20next%20generation%20telecommunications%2C%20and%20green%20energy%20applications%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20White%20House%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20two%20leaders%20praised%20combined%20efforts%20to%20facilitate%20resilient%2C%20secure%2C%20and%20sustainable%20semiconductor%20supply%20chains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20space%20technology%20sector%2C%20the%20two%20leaders%20welcomed%20the%20progress%20towards%20the%20first%20joint%20effort%20by%20NASA%20and%20ISRO%20to%20conduct%20scientific%20research%20onboard%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-modi-us-visit-as-pm-narendra-modi-and-joe-biden-hold-bilateral-talks-a-mega-drone-deal-firms-up-6620448%5C%22%3EREAD%3A%C2%A0As%20PM%20Modi%20And%20Joe%20Biden%20Hold%20Bilateral%20Talks%2C%20A%20Mega%20Drone%20Deal%20Firms%20Up%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImpetus%20To%20Defence%20Ties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20president%20welcomed%20the%20progress%20in%20India%20completing%20the%20procurement%20of%2031%20General%20Atomics%20MQ-9B%20(16%20Sky%20Guardian%20and%2015%20Sea%20Guardian)%20remotely%20piloted%20aircraft%20and%20their%20associated%20equipment%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20these%20will%20enhance%20the%20intelligence%2C%20surveillance%20and%20reconnaissance%20capabilities%20of%20India's%20armed%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20leaders%20recognised%20the%20progress%20under%20the%20US-India%20Defense%20Industrial%20Cooperation%20Roadmap%2C%20including%20ongoing%20collaboration%20to%20advance%20priority%20co-production%20arrangements%20for%20jet%20engines%2C%20munitions%2C%20and%20ground%20mobility%20systems.%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20President%20Biden%20also%20welcomed%20efforts%20to%20expand%20defence%20industrial%20partnerships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Biden%20welcomed%20India's%20decision%20to%20set%20a%20uniform%20Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax%20(GST)%20of%205%20per%20cent%20on%20the%20maintenance%2C%20repair%2C%20and%20overhaul%20(MRO)%20sector%2C%20including%20on%20all%20aircraft%20and%20aircraft%20engine%20parts%20thereby%20simplifying%20the%20tax%20structure%20and%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20building%20a%20strong%20ecosystem%20for%20MRO%20services%20in%20India.%20The%20Leaders%20also%20encouraged%20the%20industry%20to%20foster%20collaboration%20and%20drive%20innovation%20to%20support%20India's%20efforts%20to%20become%20a%20leading%20aviation%20hub%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20White%20House%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Leaders%20hailed%20the%20teaming%20agreement%20on%20the%20C-130J%20Super%20Hercules%20aircraft%20recently%20signed%20between%20Lockheed%20Martin%20and%20Tata%20Advanced%20Systems%20Limited%2C%20the%20two%20companies%20that%20co-chair%20the%20U.S.-India%20CEO%20Forum.%20Building%20on%20longstanding%20industry%20cooperation%2C%20this%20agreement%20will%20establish%20a%20new%20Maintenance%2C%20Repair%20and%20Overhaul%20(MRO)%20facility%20in%20India%20to%20support%20the%20readiness%20of%20the%20Indian%20fleet%20and%20global%20partners%20who%20operate%20the%20C-130%20Super%20Hercules%20aircraft%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20marks%20a%20significant%20step%20in%20US-India%20cooperation%20in%20the%20defence%20and%20aerospace%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-us-to-elevate-bilateral-ties-to-expand-clean-energy-supply-chains-6621420%5C%22%3EREAD%3A%20India%2C%20US%20To%20Elevate%20Bilateral%20Ties%20To%20Expand%20Clean%20Energy%20Supply%20Chains%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3