l%20get%20angry.%20If%20you%20had%20a%20boy%2C%20we%20would%20accept%20it%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20dismissed%20this%20as%20a%20one-off%20incident%2C%20refusing%20to%20let%20it%20spoil%20his%20celebratory%20mood.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20when%20I%20started%20distributing%20sweets%20in%20the%20village%2C%20I%20realised%20there%20was%20a%20serious%20problem.%20First%20of%20all%2C%20people%20would%20assume%20that%20my%20distributing%20sweets%20meant%20I%20had%20a%20baby%20boy.%20So%20they%20would%20congratulate%20me%20on%20it.%E2%80%9D%20When%20Jaglan%20told%20them%20he%20had%20become%20a%20father%20to%20a%20baby%20girl%2C%20their%20responses%20were%20usually%20consolatory.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EKoi%20baat%20nahi%2C%20agli%20baar%20ladka%20hoga%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Don%E2%80%99t%20worry.%20Next%20time%20you%20will%20get%20a%20son).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FrA-F2BWnHmk%3Fsi%3DN_7a_Xus1lNQBnDd%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20how%20would%20Jaglan%20respond%20to%20these%20unwarranted%20sympathies%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20went%20and%20bought%20more%20%3Cem%3Emithai%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20celebrated%20for%20a%20month%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%20%E2%80%9CThen%20I%20went%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F244172%2Fchushul-village-ladakh-doctor-jigmet-wangchuk-line-of-actual-control-india-china-border-coronavirus-hero-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evillage%20health%20centre%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20check%20on%20the%20sex%20ratio.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20832%20females%20per%201%2C000%20males%20in%202011.%20Some%20fact-checking%20on%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20sex%20ratio%20through%20the%20years%20tells%20me%20Jaglan%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20been%20surprised%20at%20the%20numbers.%20The%20state%20has%20been%20(in)famous%20for%20having%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20sex%20ratios%20in%20India%20%E2%80%94%20a%20problem%20compounded%20by%20patriarchal%20mindsets%20prevalent%20in%20North%20India%20where%20raising%20a%20girl%20has%20sacrificial%20connotations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%202023%20statistics%20point%20out%2C%20that%20mindsets%20are%20seeing%20a%20shift%20%E2%80%94%20there%20were%20916%20females%20per%201%2C000%20males.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20however%2C%20Jaglan%20was%20horrified.%20He%20intended%20to%20discuss%20this%20issue%20with%20women%20at%20the%20next%20%3Cem%3Egram%20sabha%3C%2Fem%3E%20meeting.%20So%2C%20you%20can%20only%20imagine%20his%20surprise%20when%20he%20discovered%20that%20Bibipur%20%3Cem%3Egram%20sabhas%3C%2Fem%3E%20were%20a%20male-dominated%20scene.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20if%20women%20had%20to%20pass%20by%20the%20spot%20where%20the%20meeting%20was%20being%20held%2C%20they%20would%20cover%20their%20heads%20in%20a%20%3Cem%3Eghoonghat%20%3C%2Fem%3E(traditional%20headscarf)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jaglan%20shares.%20The%20general%20consensus%20was%20that%20women%20were%20incapable%20of%20making%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349644%2Fcleanest-villages-of-india-mawlynnong-majuli-yana-nako-piplantri-khonoma-chitkul-dawar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evillage-level%20decisions%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20power%20of%20autonomy%20rested%20with%20the%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-3-1726842213.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sunil%20Jaglan%20encouraged%20women%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20khap%20panchayats%20in%20Bibipur%20to%20participate%20in%20village%20decisions%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-3-1726842213.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-3-1726842213-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-3-1726842213-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-3-1726842213-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsunil-jaglan-3-1726842213-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366953%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESunil%20Jaglan%20encouraged%20women%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20%3Cem%3Ekhap%20panchayats%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Bibipur%20to%20participate%20in%20village%20decisions.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirm%20in%20his%20resolve%20to%20change%20this%20chauvinist%20mentality%2C%20Jaglan%20says%20he%20began%20urging%20women%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20%3Cem%3Echaupals%20%3C%2Fem%3E(village%20meetings)%2C%20supported%20by%20his%20wife%2C%20sisters%2C%20and%20mother.%20%E2%80%9CIn%202012%2C%20we%20set%20up%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20women%20%3Cem%3Egram%20sabhas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20The%20ripple%20effect%20this%20had%20was%20tremendous%2C%20and%20Jaglan%20decided%20to%20go%20a%20step%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20hosted%20a%20%3Cem%3Ekhap%20panchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%202012%20in%20Bibipur.%20An%20unofficial%20meeting%20of%20clans%20across%20villages%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekhap%20panchayats%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20historically%20headed%20and%20attended%20by%20men.%20But%20the%20one%20that%20Jaglan%20hosted%20saw%202%2C000%20women%20from%20across%20India%20convene%20to%20discuss%20the%20issues%20that%20oppressed%20their%20female%20counterparts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20historic%20win!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20issues%20discussed%20