C).%20One%20of%20his%20responsibilities%20was%20checking%20petrol%20adulteration%20at%20petrol%20pumps.%20He%20set%20out%20on%20a%20tour%20of%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20district%20in%20November%202005.%20He%20found%20anomalies%2C%20for%20the%20second%20time%2C%20at%20the%20Mittal%20Automobile%20Petrol%20Pump%20and%20was%20about%20to%20take%20measures%20to%20seal%20it.%20On%20the%20night%20of%2019%20November%2C%20he%20was%20murdered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManjunath%E2%80%99s%20family%2C%20who%20were%20attending%20a%20family%20function%20in%20Chennai%2C%20were%20shocked%20beyond%20words.%20How%20could%20they%20even%20begin%20to%20fathom%20such%20an%20unjust%20shooting%20%E2%80%94%20where%20their%20son%E2%80%99s%20life%20was%20cut%20short%20for%20simply%20standing%20up%20for%20what%20was%20right%3F%20As%20they%20grappled%20with%20the%20loss%20of%20their%2027-year-old%20son%2C%20the%20news%20sent%20shockwaves%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20hundred%20kilometres%20away%2C%20in%20Mysuru%2C%20a%20young%20couple%2C%20Anjali%20Mullatti%20and%20H%20Jaishankar%2C%20watched%20the%20news%20unfold%20on%20their%20TV%20screens.%20As%20IIM%20alumni%20themselves%2C%20they%20were%20shocked.%20There%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20anger%2C%20grief%2C%20and%20frustration%20within%20the%20IIM%20alumni%20groups%20across%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20Calcutta%2C%20and%20Lucknow%20%E2%80%94%20the%20four%20IIMs%20at%20that%20time.%20While%20many%20vented%20their%20grief%20and%20anger%2C%20no%20one%20seemed%20to%20be%20doing%20anything%20on%20the%20ground.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnjali%20and%20Jaishankar%20decided%20they%20would%20take%20action%20if%20no%20one%20else%20did.%20Their%20efforts%20led%20them%20to%20Kamini%20Jaiswal%2C%20a%20prominent%20Supreme%20Court%20lawyer%2C%20who%20connected%20them%20with%20criminal%20lawyer%20I%20B%20Singh%20in%20Lucknow.%20Thus%20began%20their%20fight%20to%20get%20justice%20for%20Manjunath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20took%20turn