%20started%2C%20we%20noticed%20that%20over%202.5%20million%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F276266%2Fdr-anil-rajvanshi-wins-padma-shri-invents-electric-rickshaw-alcohol-stove%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelectric%20rickshaws%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India%20were%20powered%20by%20lead-acid%20batteries%2C%20serving%20nearly%2070%20million%20people%20for%20first%20and%20last-mile%20commutes.%20We%20recognised%20that%20high%20upfront%20costs%20were%20a%20significant%20barrier%20to%20adopting%20electric%20vehicles%20in%20a%20cost-conscious%20market%20like%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Pulkit%2C%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLead%20acid%20batteries%20require%20replacement%20every%20six%20months%2C%20making%20it%20a%20recurring%20capital%20expenditure%20problem%20for%20drivers.%20Moreover%2C%20drivers%20often%20spend%2010%20to%2012%20hours%20every%20night%20charging%20their%20batteries%20and%20another%203%20to%204%20hours%20to%20top%20it%20up%20during%20the%20day.%20Our%20goal%20was%20to%20upgrade%20the%20existing%20solution%20with%20better%20technology.%20Battery%20swapping%20emerged%20as%20the%20solution%2C%20as%20it%20eliminates%20the%20need%20for%20end%20users%20to%20own%20the%20battery%2C%20reducing%20upfront%20costs%20by%20as%20much%20as%2040%25%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20multiple%20ventures%20at%20the%20time%20that%20decided%20to%20get%20into%20the%20business%20of%20manufacturing%20EVs%20and%20chargers%2C%20Pulkit%20and%20Siddharth%20ventured%20into%20battery-swapping%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20manufacturing%20chargers%20and%20vehicles%20is%20an%20exciting%20field%2C%20we%20chose%20to%20focus%20on%20addressing%20key%20challenges%20such%20as%20range%20anxiety%2C%20charging%20downtime%2C%20and%20high%20costs.%20By%20partnering%20with%20over%20ten%20leading%20OEMs%2