FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-17-at-18.45.16-1-min-1726581377-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-17-at-18.45.16-1-min-1726581377-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-17-at-18.45.16-1-min-1726581377-1536x1023.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-17-at-18.45.16-1-min-1726581377-150x100.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366299%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShreyovi%E2%80%99s%20favourite%20subjects.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShreyovi%20captured%20these%20nilgais%20during%20the%20monsoon%20in%20Bharatpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20Courtesy%20Shreyovi%20Mehta%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726582732000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fshreyovi-1726580937.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D366242%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shreyovi%20Mehta%20is%20a%20runner-up%20at%20the%20Natural%20History%20Museum%2C%20London%E2%80%99s%2060th%20Wildlife%20Photographer%20of%20the%20Year%20award.%20She%20grew%20up%20accompanying%20her%20parents%20in%20national%20parks%20and%20wildlife%20safaris%20as%20they%20ran%20a%20wildlife%20photo%20tourism%20company%2C%20igniting%20her%20love%20for%20photography%20and%20wildlife.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A104%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F366242%2Fshreyovi-mehta-shivang-mehta-wildlife-photographer-nature-wanderers-natural-history-museum%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%228%20Best%20Dhabas%20To%20Save%20on%20Your%20Maps%20for%20the%20Next%20Road%20Trip%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EI%20distinctly%20recall%20a%202019%20college%20road%20trip%20to%20Kasara%20which%20lies%20along%20the%20Mumbai-Nashik%20route.%20The%20plan%20was%20an%20overnight%20trek%20to%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Sandhan%20Valley%20(also%20known%20as%20the%20Valley%20of%20Shadows).%20We%20decided%20to%20fuel%20up%20before%20commencing%20the%20long%20walk%20through%20the%20ravine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20local%20food%20joint%2C%20piping%20hot%20Maggi%2C%20%3Cem%3Esamosas%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20savoury%20Indian%20pastry)%2C%20%3Cem%3Evada%20pavs%3C%2Fem%3E%20(deep%20fried%20potato%20dumplings%20in%20bread)%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Echai%20%3C%2Fem%3Eoccupied%20the%20length%20and%20breadth%20of%20the%20ricketty%20table%20as%2017%20hungry%20adolescents%20feasted%20to%20their%20heart%E2%80%99s%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManners%20and%20etiquette%20waltzed%20out%20through%20the%20window%20as%20we%20smacked%20our%20lips%20and%20licked%20the%20spicy%20Maharashtrian%20garlic%20%3Cem%3Echutney%20%3C%2Fem%3Eoff%20our%20fingers.%20It%20became%20clear%20to%20me%20why%20since%20time%20immemorial%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360331%2Fnational-highway-restaurants-food-joints-expressway-karnal-haveli-amrik-sukhdev-azad-hind-dhaba%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Edhabas%20%3C%2Fem%3E(roadside%20food%20stalls)%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20the%20first%20choice%20of%20truck%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresumably%2C%20the%20first%20instances%20of%20%3Cem%3Edhabas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eappeared%20around%20the%20middle%20of%20the%2020th%20century%20on%20Grand%20Trunk%20Road%20(one%20of%20Asia%E2%80%99s%20oldest%20roads%20that%20connects%20Central%20Asia%20to%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent).%20I%20can%20vividly%20imagine%20a%20bunch%20of%20truckers%20sitting%20around%20on%20%3Cem%3Echarpaayis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(cots)%2C%20digging%20into%20%3Cem%3Eparanthas%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20Punjabi%20speciality)%2C%20and%20gulping%20down%20glasses%2