%20we%20consume%20daily%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20when%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20our%20diet%20is%20%3Cem%3Eroti%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20rice.%20Looking%20at%20the%20anaemia%20and%20stunting%20data%20of%20our%20country%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20we%20do%20not%20get%20enough%20nutrients%20from%20the%20food%20we%20eat.%20I%20strongly%20believe%20that%20nutrition%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20luxury%20but%20a%20right%20for%20us%20all%20Indians.%20It%E2%80%99s%20something%20everyone%20deserves%20access%20to%2C%20and%20cannot%20be%20a%20privilege%20for%20a%20few.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERealising%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20improve%20crop%20nutrition%20naturally%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20fortify%20seeds%20of%20crops%20such%20as%20maize%2C%20paddy%2C%20wheat%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F296561%2Fmahalingam-govindaraj-scientist-develops-first-biofortified-pearl-millet-bajra-wins-award%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinger%20millets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20essential%20nutrients%20like%20zinc%2C%20iron%2C%20manganese%2C%20boron%2C%20and%20copper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20understanding%20led%20to%20the%20birth%20of%20Greenday%20in%20January%202020%2C%20aiming%20to%20bring%20systemic%20innovation%20and%20enhance%20crop%20nutrition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EImproving%20nutritional%20value%20through%20biofortification%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vision%20of%20Greenday%2C%20Prateek%20says%2C%20was%20simple%20yet%20impactful.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20improve%20the%20nutritional%20quality%20of%20crops%20while%20empowering%20farmers%20economically.%20By%20encouraging%20the%20shift%20from%20traditional%20seeds%20to%20biofortified%20seeds%2C%20farmers%20were%20not%20only%20able%20to%20enhance%20their%20income%20through%20premium%20pricing%20but%20also%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20addressing%20widespread%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20