ecided%20to%20create%20something%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnehal-shah-1726490018.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nehal%20with%20her%20family%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnehal-shah-1726490018.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnehal-shah-1726490018-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnehal-shah-1726490018-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnehal-shah-1726490018-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnehal-shah-1726490018-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366071%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENehal%20with%20her%20family.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%202.5%20years%20old%2C%20she%20took%20her%20son%20on%20a%20camping%20trip%20to%20Kamshet%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20dispelling%20several%20myths%20along%20the%20way.%20That%20first%20adventure%20was%20a%20game%20changer%2C%20revealing%20a%20new%20side%20of%20her%20child%20and%20sparking%20an%20idea.%20Inspired%20by%20his%20excitement%2C%20Nehal%20founded%20%E2%80%98Heart%20%26amp%3B%20Soil%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Mumbai-based%20venture%20that%20curates%20nature-based%20travel%20experiences.%20It%20offers%20wilderness%20excursions%2C%20farming%20activities%2C%20treks%2C%20nature%20trails%2C%20camping%2C%20stargazing%20nights%2C%20and%20rural%20visits%2C%20providing%20families%20with%20enriching%20outdoor%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202016%2C%20Heart%20%26amp%3B%20Soil%20has%20helped%20over%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nor